    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/af29ca59b3cb794e65a46ca82cf795eb.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=67 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/1deac1017f542ed99a5bce2ad89df3e3.poster.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/1deac1017f542ed99a5bce2ad89df3e3.webm?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/1deac1017f542ed99a5bce2ad89df3e3.mp4?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《按右键启动翻译器》是一款由鞘猫生态与行为学实验研究中心开发的一款横版剧情向语言解谜游戏。该游戏获 2024 中国大学生游戏开发创作大赛 CUSGA 最佳解谜游戏奖。<br><br>“你”所收留的流浪猫“小白”失踪了……<br><br>“你”急忙下楼寻找，直到你触碰到了一幅之前没有注意到的壁画。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/5349820407a59df0bc9fa24559de6755.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=67 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/be4d106bfcaf323b0618f26d2a04a774.poster.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/be4d106bfcaf323b0618f26d2a04a774.webm?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/be4d106bfcaf323b0618f26d2a04a774.mp4?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>突如其来的异世界穿越……无法理解的古怪文字……似由“猫”与“章鱼”络合的异族生物……<br><br>“你”马上意识到，这次找猫的旅途只是庞大异世界风物志异中的小小注脚。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/5c07b0039d6c15b67abe3cb33bfec305.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=67 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/e76a20af086b7eed5bf4e6361bb3028e.poster.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/e76a20af086b7eed5bf4e6361bb3028e.webm?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/e76a20af086b7eed5bf4e6361bb3028e.mp4?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索“鞘猫”们生存的大地，或者可以叫它们“章鱼猫”。解开这座孤岛上的各种秘密，与原住民深入交流，学会它们的语言。打听到的传说揭示了“创世”、“灾厄”、“英雄”，而所有的线索指向了岛屿中心那座濒临崩溃的火山……<br><br>古老传说的预言但存残篇，异世的勇士拯救传说的英雄……与世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/3925b155f25782496c74875ce6cae749.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=67 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/4babde0977ff39a440577b6c57348ef1.poster.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/4babde0977ff39a440577b6c57348ef1.webm?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/4babde0977ff39a440577b6c57348ef1.mp4?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>章鱼猫们没有发声器官，因此，“说话”的方式是靠调动自己的器官，在身体上浮现自己要“说”的文字。留心一路上的告示贴示，记忆每一次的解谜，多多与章鱼猫们交流，用潜水服上的全息翻译器推理出章猫语的全部含义，时时编辑词典里每个字符的含义，用翻译器的其他功能帮助你回忆，随时更正。<br><br>“为了拯救世界，这下不得不学习一门二外了。”<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/7c57c299da3c194275f15e5e877e8ee3.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=67 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/f2f0110f0b8fe969c36a1f14f24c4a1b.poster.avif?t=1761364276\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/f2f0110f0b8fe969c36a1f14f24c4a1b.webm?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128590/extras/f2f0110f0b8fe969c36a1f14f24c4a1b.mp4?t=1761364276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>漫步像素的山径、高塔、集市，领略绮丽风光，聆听独具特色的原创原声带，沉浸在“几乎”是幻象的世界里。<br><br><br><br>————<br>QQ 交流群：725518765",
